OL,3,CMilitary families to be compensated
OL,4,Cfor serious water outage after MoD
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FOver 100 military families who were
OL,8,Faffected by a serious water outage in
OL,9,FApril have been told they will finally
OL,10,Freceive compensation after suffering
OL,11,Fdelays.
OL,13,FThousands of people living in Plymouth
OL,14,Fwere left with low pressure or no
OL,15,Fsupply for several days, following a
OL,16,Fburst water main.
OL,18,FThis included 169 homes of military
OL,19,Fstaff and their families.
