OL,4,Cfor serious water outage after MoD
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FAfter lobbying on the issue he's now
OL,8,Freceived confirmation from Al Cairns,
OL,9,FMinister for Veterans & People that
OL,10,Fmilitary households affected will
OL,11,Freceive compensation totalling #42,250.
OL,13,FHe said, "This has always been about
OL,14,Fmuch more than the money, it has been
OL,15,Fabout upholding the clear principle of
OL,16,Fthe Armed Forces Covenant: that no one
OL,17,Fshould be disadvantaged by dint of
OL,18,Ftheir service."
